# Libraries (concise)

Full audit: `documentation/update-libraries.md`. Credits: `scripts/generate-credits.php` → `licenses/Credits.html`.

## Composer (PHP runtime)

| Library | Purpose | Used in |
|---------|---------|---------|
| Yii 2 | Framework (DB, log, migrations) | `src/Db/*`, `src/Log/*`, `config/console.php` |
| Smarty | Template engine | `src/Runtime/CRM_Viewer.php`, `layouts/**/*.tpl` |
| PHPMailer | Outbound SMTP | `src/Email/Mailer.php`, Mail SMTP/IMAP |
| HTML Purifier 4.19 | Server HTML sanitization | `src/Security/Purifier.php`, `Vtiger_Request`, UiTypes |
| PhpSpreadsheet | Excel export | `QuickExport.php`, `Reports/ReportRun.php` |
| webklex/php-imap | IMAP mail client | `Mail/Imap/*`, mail cron |
| rmccue/requests | HTTP client | RSS, SMS providers, PBX, system warnings |
| Recurr | RRULE → calendar instances | `Events/Models/RecuringEvents.php`, cron |
| ANTLR4 PHP | Workflow condition parser | `src/Events/VTEventConditionParser*.php` |
| libphonenumber-for-php | Phone normalize on import | `RecruitmentApplication/.../PhoneNormalizer.php` |
| Linfo | Server diagnostics | `Settings/ConfReport/` |

## PHP bundled (not Composer)

| Library | Purpose | Used in |
|---------|---------|---------|
| SabreDAV 3.1.3 | CalDAV/CardDAV | `src/Api/dav.php`, API CalDAV/CardDAV models |
| HTTP_Session | Webservice sessions (legacy) | `Webservices/SessionManager.php`, `Vtiger_Session.php` |
| CSRF-magic | Form CSRF tokens | `WebUI.php`, `config/csrf_config.php`, entrypoints |
| RSS & Atom Feeds | RSS dashboard widget | `RSSFeeds/Feed.php`, Rss module |

## Global JS/CSS (authenticated pages)

Registered in `src/Base/Controllers/BaseViewController.php` + `src/Modules/Base/Views/Basic.php`. Behavior: `public/libraries/resources/app.js`, `helper.js`.

| Library | Purpose |
|---------|---------|
| jQuery 2.1.4 + Migrate | DOM/AJAX foundation (EOL) |
| jQuery UI | Widgets (sortable, dialog, …) |
| Bootstrap 3 | Primary UI framework (EOL) |
| Font Awesome 6 | Icons |
| Select2 | Enhanced `<select>` |
| Perfect Scrollbar | Panel/modal scrollbars |
| jQuery Validation Engine | Client form validation |
| PNotify | Toasts |
| Bootbox | Bootstrap modals |
| blockUI | AJAX loading overlay |
| PJAX | Partial page navigation |
| DOMPurify 3.4.10 | Client HTML sanitization |
| Input Mask, Mousetrap, Datepicker, ClockPicker | Masks, shortcuts, date/time pickers |

Sync vendored JS: `npm run dompurify:sync`, `npm run ckeditor:sync`, `npm run bootstrap:sync`.

## Feature JS (loaded per view)

| Library | Purpose | Typical screens |
|---------|---------|-----------------|
| CKEditor 4.22.1 | Rich text (OSS; not 4.25 LTS) | Workflows, Dashboard, `CkEditor.js` |
| CodeMirror 5 | Code/HTML templates | Email/Document/Template element editors |
| DataTables | Sortable tables | Settings lists, KB tree, trees |
| FullCalendar + Moment | Calendars | Calendar, Home, DashBoard, OSSTimeControl |
| Gridster | Dashboard widget grid | Home, DashBoard |
| jqPlot, Flot | Charts | Dashboards, Reports, detail charts |
| jsTree | Trees | Settings Menu, KB, tree popups |
| Leaflet (+ cluster, awesome-markers) | Maps | Detail map, OpenStreetMap modal |
| html2canvas | Screenshot for issue report | `Basic.php` (HelpDesk) |
| clipboard.js | Copy buttons | Template editors, OSSPasswords, Settings |

## npm dev only

`terser`, `clean-css-cli` — minify; `bootstrap`, `dompurify`, `ckeditor4` — upstream for `*:sync` scripts.

## Rollout (June 2026)

Phase 0 ✅ cleanup (removed unused Composer deps). Phase 1 ✅ DOMPurify, CKEditor 4.22.1, HTML Purifier 4.19. Next: Phase 2 Composer patches — see `documentation/update-libraries.md`.
